-- Emirates NBD Expects Dubai World Debt Resolution in `Few Weeks,' CEO Says
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-04-26T10:51:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/emirates-nbd-expects-dubai-world-debt-resolution-in-few-weeks-ceo-says.html

          
          
             Emirates NBD PJSC, the United Arab
Emirates’ biggest bank by assets, expects a resolution to Dubai
World’s debt restructuring in a “few weeks,” Chief Executive
Officer Rick Pudner said in a conference call today.  
 Negotiations are making good progress, Pudner said.
Emirates NBD is one the biggest lenders to state-owned Dubai
World, which is restructuring $24.8 billion of debt.  
